=You are a job market analyst and career advisor specializing in IT roles. I scraped three job boards for ServiceNow Developer and SRE positions in India posted in the last 24 hours.

**LinkedIn Results:**
{{ JSON.stringify($('TinyFish: LinkedIn Jobs').first().json, null, 2) }}

**Naukri Results:**
{{ JSON.stringify($('TinyFish: Naukri Jobs').first().json, null, 2) }}

**Indeed Results:**
{{ JSON.stringify($('TinyFish: Indeed Jobs').first().json, null, 2) }}

Now do the following:

## STEP 1: Deduplicate
Remove duplicate job postings that appear on multiple platforms. Match by company name + similar job title + same location. When duplicates exist, keep the one with the most complete information and note which platforms it appeared on.

## STEP 2: Score Each Job (1-100)
Score each UNIQUE job on these weighted criteria:
- **Role Relevance (30 pts)**: How closely does the title/description match 'ServiceNow Developer', 'ServiceNow Architect', 'ServiceNow Admin', or 'Site Reliability Engineer'? Penalize generic IT roles that just mention ServiceNow as one of many skills.
- **Company Quality (20 pts)**: Is it a well-known product company, Big 4 consultancy, Fortune 500, or top-tier startup? Penalize unknown staffing agencies.
- **Compensation Signal (15 pts)**: Is salary disclosed? Is it competitive? Higher score for transparency and good ranges.
- **Location Fit (15 pts)**: Hyderabad or Remote scores highest. Bangalore, Pune, Mumbai score well. Other cities score lower.
- **Growth Potential (10 pts)**: Does it mention learning, certifications, career growth, or cutting-edge work (AI/ML integration, DevOps, platform engineering)?
- **Recency (10 pts)**: Posted in last few hours scores higher than 1 day ago.

## STEP 3: Return Top 10
Return ONLY the top 10 jobs sorted by score (highest first).

For each job, format EXACTLY like this (this will be sent to WhatsApp, use WhatsApp formatting):

*#{rank} — {jobTitle}* (Score: {score}/100)
🏢 {company}
📍 {location} | 💼 {jobType}
💰 {salaryRange}
🎯 {experienceLevel}
🔧 {top 3-4 skills}
📋 {one-line why this job scored high}
🔗 {jobUrl}
📌 Found on: {platforms where it appeared}

After listing all 10, add:

---
📊 *Today's Market Snapshot*
• Total jobs found: {count across all platforms}
• Duplicates removed: {count}
• Top hiring companies today: {top 3 companies by number of openings}
• Most demanded skills: {top 5 skills across all postings}
• Salary range observed: {min} - {max} (where disclosed)
• 🟢 Hot locations: {cities with most openings}

💡 _Pro tip: {one actionable career tip based on today's data, e.g., 'ITSM skills are in high demand today — consider CSA certification if you haven't already'}_

